{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/snyopsis.png?t=1584938812\" /><br>Spend a day in a rainy castle and befriend, or fall for, a non-binary dragon.<br><br>Stars and Snowdrops is a short, atmospheric visual novel played from the perspective of Princess Kovida.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/characters.png?t=1584938812\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/portrait_Animated_3.gif?t=1584938812\" /><br>This spoiled princess has a lot of growing to do in a very short amount of time, but ultimately her heart shines like the stars.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/Frel_teaser2.jpg?t=1584938812\" /><br><br>The kingdom's royal adviser, Frel, who kelps Kovi along her path.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/sahar_teaser2.jpg?t=1584938812\" /><br><br>A nobleman from the kingdom, Sahar has a few 'curious' ideals that he lives by.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/hatsu_womp.jpg?t=1584938812\" /><br><br>A guardswoman from the capital, Hatsu is as stoic as her armor.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1013820/extras/features.png?t=1584938812\" /><br>- Three body sizes and skin tones for Princess Kovi for you to choose from. <br>- Gorgeous, animated backgrounds and characters.<br>- All characters are fully voiced by incredibly talented voice actors.<br>- A short, refreshing story with atmospheric ambiance, music and sound effects.<br>- Small conversation options that help dictate Kovi's personality.<br>- A very cute adviser~